com.cerner.beadledom.avro

Class AvroJacksonModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.Module
      • com.cerner.beadledom.avro.AvroJacksonModule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.fasterxml.jackson.core.Versioned

    public class AvroJacksonModule
extends com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.Module
    A Jackson Module that provides serialization and deserialization of Avro objects extending from SpecificRecordBase.

    To use this module, register it with the ObjectMapper. An instance of BuildInfo is required to instantiate a AvroJacksonModule.
